data.description: Fantastic opportunity to own this ground-level condominium in Windsor Gardens! You'll be delighted by the appealing open layout showcasing laminate flooring, 2 spacious bedrooms, and a full bathroom. The open-concept kitchen includes track lighting, plenty of cabinets, sleek stainless steel appliances, mosaic tile backsplash, & a peninsula with a breakfast bar. Both bedrooms have been newly carpeted and offer ample closet space to suit your storage needs. Grab your favorite drink & relax in the sunroom, offering an excellent view of the Community. Great location right across from the clubhouse, fitness center, restaurant, pool, & parks. This move-in-ready gem won't last long on the market! Windsor Gardens is a 55+ Community!
